        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寄食岂是长久策，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无计谋食受饥饿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四少年内同笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见一群少年笑呵呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾勇、四少年同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾勇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位，你们瞧韩信这小子，身跨宝剑，倒仿佛是个武术家似的，待我赶罗赶罗"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾勇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾勇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "韩信，你身带宝剑，敢给我一下子吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我素无仇恨，何能如此！"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾勇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要不干的话，那就从我这儿——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾勇指胯下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾勇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "钻过去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（韩信寻思。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，我就钻了过去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（韩信钻。四少年同笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四少年",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得了，咱们走吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾勇、四少年同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蛟龙失水遭虾戏，虎落平阳被犬欺。燕雀怎晓鸿鹄志，暂且忍耐待来时。"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
