    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "二村妇",
        "村妇乙",
        "村妇甲",
        "漂母"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（漂母上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤苦伶仃，食己力，且度残生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "生来命不幸，半世守清贫。儿夫早丧命，抛下未亡人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老身吴氏。久以漂洗为生，故人皆称我“漂母”。真名实姓反无人知晓。膝下"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无有儿女，丈夫去世，抛下老身一人。上无片瓦，下午立锥。且喜身体粗健，"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "每日在这淮阴城外洗衣为生，倒也清闲自在。每日清晨，同村中贫苦夫人，结"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伴前去漂洗。看今日天气晴和，不免收拾衣衫，前去洗濯一番便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叹孤身苦奔忙无依无靠，"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可怜我终日里漂洗在城壕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寸草不生少禾苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那时节有何人葬埋在荒郊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二村妇同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "村妇甲",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "每日苦勤劳，"
        },
        {
          "character": "村妇乙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "漂洗在城壕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "村妇甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大嫂，今儿个漂母怎么没找咱们去呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "村妇乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也许她不洗啦，咱们找找她去。走着走着。到啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二村妇",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "漂母在家吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（漂母开门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是二位娘子，请到里面。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二村妇",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "您今儿个怎么没找我们去呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "收拾已毕，就要前去，你们倒先来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二村妇",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们只当您不去洗了哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位说哪里话来，想你二人有公婆照顾，有丈夫倚靠，挣来漂洗之钱，自己零"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用；老身孤苦伶仃，无倚无靠，每日用度，全仗自己劳力，哪有无故不去漂洗"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "之理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "村妇甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大娘，你说什么，我们有公婆照顾？依我说，还是您一个人无拘无束好。想我"
        },
        {
          "character": "村妇甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那公婆年已老迈，早晚还要服侍他们，若不是往家里挣钱，我拿婆婆早就不叫"
        },
        {
          "character": "村妇甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我去洗啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "村妇乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要说有丈夫有倚靠，我拿丈夫喝两盅儿酒，动不动就发脾气，开口骂，举手打，"
        },
        {
          "character": "村妇乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说什么：振作夫纲。耐心忍受，还则罢了；稍一反抗，乡里中就落个“不贤”"
        },
        {
          "character": "村妇乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "之名。就是我挣的钱，也大半供他喝酒啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘子啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你二人说此话情理固顺，"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎奈这尘世中礼数约人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天色不早，我们去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（漂母、二村妇同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
