    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "他耐等文王把贤访",
        "你在河边来垂钓",
        "你要学周朝姜吕望",
        "小生日后鹏程奋",
        "我本是名人后性情明正",
        "我看你相貌非凡品",
        "昔日里伍子胥沿街讨饭",
        "村妇甲",
        "漂母",
        "甘罗秦朝为官宦",
        "眼望河边离不远",
        "这是老身良言劝",
        "韩信"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（韩信持钓竿上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "英雄困顿负壮志，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "垂钓充饥且耐时。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天哪，天！想俺韩信乃堂堂男子，落落丈夫，只落得这般光景，咳，困煞英雄"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恨天公作事无分晓，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说什么贫和富命里相招？"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我好似风中絮浪里萍飘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到老来竟落得万载名标。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到何日遇明主才放光豪？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（韩信下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "内唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家中贫寒当勤俭，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二村妇、漂母同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "年迈身衰靠苍天。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "沉沉碧水养红莲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼望河边离不远"
        },
        {
          "character": "村妇甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "您在这儿，我们到那边儿洗去啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请便。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二村妇同下。韩信上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "饥饿难忍心志迷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抬头不辨路东西。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "填于沟壑有谁知！"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳！只望钓得几尾鱼儿，换取饭食也好充饥；怎奈天寒水浅，鱼不上钩，好生"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晦气。一路行来，腹饥难忍，叫我哪里去讨？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（韩信看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔呼呀！那旁有一老妈妈，待俺上前哀告于她，倘若肯赐一饭，也未可知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老妈妈在上，小生有礼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公少礼。有何见教？"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小生流落无依，腹中饥饿；老妈妈如有残羹剩饭，望求方便方便！"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噢！原来是饥寒之人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "惭愧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是老身带来的冷饭，相公如不嫌弃，请用了吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢妈妈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请用。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "富庶黄金何足贵，饥寒一饭最难求。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，你就请用吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一碗饭不过是随时方便，"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看他不像个无为少年。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大丈夫不逢时难免今天。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昔日里伍子胥沿街讨饭"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢妈妈活命之恩！"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "些许小事，何足挂齿。你且少待。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住！看这相公，相貌不凡，为何落在乞讨之中？待我仔细问他一番便了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大相公进前来我有话论，"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你听我把言语细说分明："
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看你不似讨饭人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看你相貌非凡品"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妈妈容禀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看你相貌非凡品"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说什么相貌非凡品，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "讲什么不似讨饭人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到如今似飘萍流转无根。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我本是名人后性情明正"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我本是名人后性情明正"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听他言果然是名门之后，"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再问你名和姓家住何村？"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我本姓韩单名信，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家门不远住淮阴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既有家该回转父母孝敬，"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为什么常在外流落飘零？"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可怜我父和母早年丧命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "并无有妻和子独自一人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看起来你就该读书上进，"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不读书去从军也好安身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文章好武艺精难疗贫困，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我只得暂忍耐再奔前程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。老身虽然贫寒，一饭尚能周济，我每日在此漂洗，你饥饿之时，只"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管前来一饱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢妈妈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多蒙妈妈救孤贫，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周济一餐值千金。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "答报今日再造恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小生日后鹏程奋"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公此言差矣！想人生在世，必须要轰轰烈烈作些惊天动地之事，落得美名，"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "流传后世，不枉生男儿七尺之躯。想你堂堂男子，青年丈夫，每日三餐，不能"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自给，甘受这饥寒之苦，岂不令人可怜？是我见你青年落魄，故以饭食相赠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公你来看，老身花甲之年，还能活上几载？岂望汝报？老身还有一言相劝，"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小生日后鹏程奋"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公听我说一遍，"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有辈古人听根源："
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十二岁陪伴在君前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "每日垂钓在河边。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八十二岁运转时来奠定周朝八百年。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "盼望明主来访你只怕是难上又加难。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你若是不听也枉然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "甘罗秦朝为官宦"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要学周朝姜吕望"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他耐等文王把贤访"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你在河边来垂钓"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是老身良言劝"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老妈妈之言，小生牢牢紧记。倘日后得志，不敢辜负妈妈之教。"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公你还是前去从军，也好替国家出力报效。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若是从军，在阵前有失，岂不白白地送了性命？"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此言差矣！你乃堂堂男子，青年丈夫，倘若从军战死沙场，也落得个名标青史，"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万古流芳。有道是："
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天下纷纷刀兵乱，称王霸业为江山。阵前敌人俱杀散，留得美名万古传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢妈妈良言劝，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "韩信自愿到军前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩信",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一饭之恩记心间。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（韩信下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "漂母",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小韩信去从戎未能轻看，"
        }
      ],
